{"ja429:0.1":"Jataka ","ja429:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja429:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja429:0.4":"3. Mahasuvajataka ","ja429:1.1":"“Dumo yada hoti phalupapanno, ","ja429:1.2":"Bhunjanti nam vihangama sampatanta; ","ja429:1.3":"Khinanti natvana dumam phalaccaye, ","ja429:1.4":"Disodisam yanti tato vihangama. ","ja429:2.1":"Cara carikam lohitatunda mamari, ","ja429:2.2":"Kim tvam suva sukkhadumamhi jhayasi; ","ja429:2.3":"Tadingha mam bruhi vasantasannibha, ","ja429:2.4":"Kasma suva sukkhadumam na rincasi”. ","ja429:3.1":"“Ye ve sakhinam sakharo bhavanti, ","ja429:3.2":"Panaccaye dukkhasukhesu hamsa; ","ja429:3.3":"Khinam akhinampi na tam jahanti, ","ja429:3.4":"Santo satam dhammamanussaranta. ","ja429:4.1":"Soham satam annatarosmi hamsa, ","ja429:4.2":"Nati ca me hoti sakha ca rukkho; ","ja429:4.3":"Tam nussahe jivikattho pahatum, ","ja429:4.4":"Khinanti natvana na hesa dhammo”. ","ja429:5.1":"“Sadhu sakkhi katam hoti, ","ja429:5.2":"metti samsati santhavo; ","ja429:5.3":"Sacetam dhammam rocesi, ","ja429:5.4":"pasamsosi vijanatam. ","ja429:6.1":"So te suva varam dammi, ","ja429:6.2":"pattayana vihangama; ","ja429:6.3":"Varam varassu vakkanga, ","ja429:6.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja429:7.1":"“Varanca me hamsa bhavam dadeyya, ","ja429:7.2":"Ayanca rukkho punarayum labhetha; ","ja429:7.3":"So sakhava phalima samvirulho, ","ja429:7.4":"Madhutthiko titthatu sobhamano”. ","ja429:8.1":"“Tam passa samma phalimam ularam, ","ja429:8.2":"Sahava te hotu udumbarena; ","ja429:8.3":"So sakhava phalima samvirulho, ","ja429:8.4":"Madhutthiko titthatu sobhamano”. ","ja429:9.1":"“Evam sakka sukhi hohi, ","ja429:9.2":"saha sabbehi natibhi; ","ja429:9.3":"Yathahamajja sukhito, ","ja429:9.4":"disvana saphalam dumam”. ","ja429:10.1":"“Suvassa ca varam datva, ","ja429:10.2":"katvana saphalam dumam; ","ja429:10.3":"Pakkami saha bhariyaya, ","ja429:10.4":"devanam nandanam vanan”ti. ","ja429:11.1":"Mahasuvajatakam tatiyam. "}